<example id="example-47a">
<para id="element-47a"><term>Problem : </term> 
The initial angular velocity of a point (in radian) on a rotating disk is 0.5 rad/s. The disk is subjected to a constant acceleration of 0. 2 
<m:math>
<m:mi> rad </m:mi>
<m:mo> / </m:mo>
<m:msup>
<m:mo> s </m:mo>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msup>
</m:math>
