</para>
<para id="element-49"><term>Solution : </term> 
Here, we need to be careful as the point reverses its direction in the third second ! For ω = 0,
</para>
<para id="element-50">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mi> ω </m:mi>
<m:mo> = </m:mo>
